                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>for younger children he might do better_do dear\n                                                  <persName>Isaac</persName><lb/> interest yourself\n                                        for us and if you think there is a better<lb/> opening in\n                                        your city or elsewhere let us know and if<lb/> a boarding\n                                        house would succeed in either place. I cannot but believe\n                                        that our merciful Father will not<lb/> suffer those to want\n                                        who so <sic>confidantly</sic> depend in<lb/> his mercy to\n                                        relieve their necessities and actively strive<lb/> with all\n                                        their energies to live—I regret my inability<lb/> at present\n                                        to pay you for those two prayer books, but<lb/> hope to do\n                                        so at some future day, and also that I<lb/> cannot afford to\n                                        be any longer a subscriber to the<lb/> publication\n                                        society—when I can renew it I will let you<lb/> know—should\n                                        any one come this way who wishes to<lb/> live\n                                                  <sic>cosher</sic> whilst <sic>her</sic> I\n                                                  <sic>shold</sic> be glad to have them<lb/> stop\n                                        with us—your Cousin <persName>Myer</persName> reports he was\n                                        engaged<lb/> to me and that I am his Cousin, so of course am\n                                        yours<lb/> he has quite a pretty daughter I am told—I need not<lb/>\n                                        <sic>as</sic> you not to expose the contents of this as I\n                                        well<lb/> know you will only do that which will be\n                                        right—</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">God bless and send you better health and\n                                        better<lb/> fortune than your poor friend</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(11)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">A. Block</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">remembrance to all friends—love <sic>“</sic>to my Aunt<lb/>\n                                        <persName>Mark's</persName> and A new house and offer my\n                                        congratulations<lb/> to them—I just recollected that I told\n                                                  <persName>Rosalie</persName><lb/> to pay you for\n                                        those books did she do<lb/> so?</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3w37mc04/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
